Direct Known Subclasses:
LogicalChi
public class Chi
extends SingleRel
Relational operator that converts a stream to a relation.

Chi is named for the Greek letter χ and pronounced 'kai'.

Chi is the inverse of Delta. For any relation R, Chi(Delta(R)) == R.
